This paper is about recommender systems, which are commonly studied in the information retrieval (cs.IR) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The proposed algorithm involves preprocessing the ratings matrix, which suggests a data science (cs.DS) component. Additionally, the algorithm aims to improve accuracy, which is a common goal in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) research. Finally, the paper deals with missing values, which is a common problem in database (cs.DB) research.
